object.customQuery:
select distinct 
    a.buildinglimitdesc, 
    a.buildingstatus, 
    a.buildinglimit, 
    a.premisesliability, 
    a.buildingclasscd, 
    a.contentsclasscd, 
    a.constructioncd, 
    a.contentslimit, 
    a.standarddeductible, 
    a.numberofapartment, 
    a.numberofapartmentscondo, 
    a.numberofapartmentsband, 
    a.numberofstories, 
    a.sqfeetarea, 
    a.sqftareaband, 
    a.numberoffamilies, 
    a.riskid, 
    a.protectionclass, 
    a.sprinklercd, 
    a.ratingterritory, 
    a.ratingterritorydesc, 
    a.individualriskpremiummod, 
    a.expensemod, 
    a.agecreditamt, 
    a.dupccreditamt, 
    a.latitude, 
    a.longitude, 
    a.buildingwindhaildeductible, 
    a.distancetoshore, 
    a.distancetoshoremile, 
    a.distancetoshorefeet, 
    a.sircoastline, 
    a.buildingclassdescription, 
    a.contentsclassdescription, 
    a.sircoastlinemile, 
    a.sircoastlinefeet, 
    a.floodzone, 
    a.elevation, 
    a.totalinsuredvalue, 
    a.riskcity, 
    a.riskpostalcd, 
    a.riskaddress, 
    a.riskcounty, 
    a.bulidingnumber, 
    a.liabilitylimit, 
    a.covapremium, 
    a.covcpremium, 
    a.cyberliabilitylimit, 
    a.commercialliabilitylimit, 
    a.onpremiseslimit, 
    a.valuablepapersrecords, 
    a.foodspoilagelimit, 
    a.fungiproperty, 
    a.demolitionlimit, 
    a.increasedcostconstructionlimit, 
    a.combdemolitioninccostlimit, 
    a.extbuildingbroadlimit, 
    a.extbuildingeqlimit, 
    a.extbuildingfloodlimit, 
    a.exteriorsignslimit, 
    a.isoearthquakelimit, 
    a.waterbackuplimit, 
    a.blanketbasisind, 
    a.personalliabilitylimit, 
    a.num_vehicles, 
    a.numofbuildingscomplex, 
    a.distancetoshoreband, 
    a.sircoastlineband, 
    a.formattedriskaddress, 
    a.formattedriskzipcode, 
    a.formattedriskcity, 
    a.formattedlatitude, 
    a.formattedlongitude, 
    a.yearbuilt, 
    a.elitepackageind, 
    a.firedistrict, 
    a.formattedstreet, 
    a.formattedcounty, 
    a.optionaldedtype, 
    a.optionalded, 
    a.perunitdeductibletype, 
    a.perunitdeductibleamt, 
    b.policykey, 
    b.carriercd, 
    b.lineofbusiness, 
    b.shellpolicyind, 
    y.displayvalue as "view_construction_year_display_value", 
    y.lo as "view_construction_year_low", 
    y.hi as "view_construction_year_high", 
    l.displayvalue as "building_limit_displayvalue", 
    l.hi  as "building_limit_high", 
    l.lo as  "building_limit_low", 
    l.parentdimid as "building_limit_parentdim_id", 
    dl.displayvalue as "content_limit_displayvalue", 
    dl.hi  as "content_limit_high", 
    dl.lo as  "content_limit_displaylow", 
    dl.parentdimid as "content_limit_parent_dim_id", 
    o.display_occupancydesc,
    o.gwoccupancycd,
    a.offpremiseslimit 
from dbo.risk a 
left join dbo."policydetail" b on a.policykey = b.policykey
left join dbo.view_construction_year y on "yearbuilt" between y.lo and y.hi
left join (
    select displayvalue, hi, lo, parentdimid
    from dbo.dim_limits_new 
    where dimid not in (-99,-88,1,25,26)
) l on buildinglimit::int between l.lo::integer and l.hi::integer
and (
    case 
        when b.lineofbusiness in ('businessowners','commercialumbrella')
            then 26
        else 25
    end
) = l.parentdimid
left join (
    select displayvalue, hi, lo, parentdimid
    from dbo.dim_limits_new 
    where dimid not in (-99,-88,1,25,26)
) dl on "contentslimit"::integer between dl.lo::integer and dl.hi::integer
and (
    case 
        when b.lineofbusiness in ('businessowners','commercialumbrella')
            then 26
        else 25
    end
) = dl.parentdimid    
left join dbo.occupancycd_ref o on o.gwoccupancycd = a."occupancycd"
where a.roweffenddt = '9999-12-31 00:00:00.000'
    and b.shellpolicyind is null

fields.name: o_Deductible
fields.expression: IIF(ISNULL(StandardDeductible), 'Unknown Policy Deductible', IIF(LENGTH(StandardDeductible) >=5, StandardDeductible, LPAD(StandardDeductible, 5, '0')))

fields.name: o_Number_Of_Apartments
fields.expression:
DECODE( TRUE
      , ISNULL(NumberOfApartment) AND NOT ISNULL(NumberOfApartmentsCondo), NumberOfApartmentsCondo
      , ISNULL(NumberOfApartment) AND ISNULL(NumberOfApartmentsCondo),NumberOfApartment, 
IIF(LENGTH(NumberOfApartment) >=3, NumberOfApartment,
LPAD(NumberOfApartment, 3, '0') ))
